Package it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.model

Class BasicTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unicam.cs.pa.jbudget105053.model.BasicTransaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasID, Transaction
    public class BasicTransaction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Transaction
    This class implements the interface Transaction and has the responsibility of managing a basic transaction. It allows to get the information related to the transaction: ID, date, total money amount, list of all the movements associated with the transaction and the list of all the tags associated to the transaction. The value obtainable with the method getTotalAmount() represents the total variation of the movements of the transaction.
    Author:
    Tommaso Catervi

        public void addMovement​(Movement movement)
        Allows to add a new Movement to the movementList as long as the given parameter is not null and doesn't already exist in the movementList. When a movement is added to the movementList, this BasicTransaction is assigned to the transaction field of that Movement. Also, the date of the added Movement is set equal to the date of this Transaction.
